These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, adventure, zombie, family
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, quad-bike, helicopter, subway
1. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
2. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
5. the person driving the subway is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person driving the helicopter##2
6. the person watching family movies is the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | family | scientific     | zombie | adventure |
| Transport     | scooter     | helicopter | subway  | quad-bike      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, blues, soul, indie
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, van, ship, roller
1. the fan of blues is on the left of the person driving the van##1
2. the person driving the roller is on the far left or far right##3
3. the fan of indie is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
4. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the van##1
5. the fan of soul is on the far right##1
6. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | trance | blues    | indie     | soul  |
| Transport     | skateboard    | ship | van | roller |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, r&b, punk, hip-hop
4 different pets are kept: goat, pony, goldfish, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the fan of r&b##3
2. the fan of r&b is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
4. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the fan of country##3
5. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the fan of punk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | r&b   | punk   | country  | hip-hop |
| Pet           | pony | guinea-pig | goldfish | goat  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, puzzles, camping, woodworking
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, indonesian, american, russian
1. the russian is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is between the person who's hobby is writing and the american##2
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is camping##3
4. the american is on the left or right of the russian##3
5. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
6. the australian is on the right of the indonesian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby         | puzzles | writing | woodworking | camping  |
| Nationality   | indonesian  | australian   | russian  | american |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, cola, water, lemonade
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, photography, puzzles, chess
1. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is photography##3
4. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
5. the person who's hobby is chess is the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | milk    | cola   | water | lemonade    |
| Hobby      | photography | skydiving | puzzles       | chess |

