4. the person driving the airplane is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | 7up | cola | water | lemonade |
| Transport   | skateboard | bike  | ship    | airplane  |

