.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, collecting, chess, cooking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, crime, zombie, sports
1. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person watching crime movies##1
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
4. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
5. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
6. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| Hobby         | cooking | chess | gardening | collecting   |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | zombie | family      | sports |

