2. the person who's sport is handball is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is handball is the owner of the goat##1
4. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
5. the owner of the mouse is on the far left or far right##3
6. the owner of the goldfish is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person who's sport is cycling##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Pet     | mouse | goldfish   | guinea-pig      | goat      |
