.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-10::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, r&b, disco, d&b
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, dutch, canadian, colombian
1. the indonesian is on the right of the dutch##1
2. the fan of disco is between the colombian and the dutch##2
3. the fan of r&b is the dutch##1
4. the canadian is on the left of the dutch##1
5. the fan of d&b is on the left or right of the indonesian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3     |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | r&b | disco      | d&b   |
| Nationality   | canadian  | dutch    | indonesian | colombian |

