.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, puzzles, cooking, collecting
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, bike, jet-ski, train
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
3. the person driving the train is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
4. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
5. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
6. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Hobby       | sudoku | cooking | collecting    | puzzles      |
| Transport   | jet-ski       | train       | bike | motorbike |

