4 different pets are kept: dog, pony, chinchilla, snake
1. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
2. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
3. the owner of the snake is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
4. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far left##1
5. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |      3      |   4    |
| Hobby   | cooking     | skydiving  | photography | collecting |
| Pet     | dog | snake | pony     | chinchilla    |

