.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-13::.
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, dutch, spanish, british
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, hedgehog, pony, snake
1. the dutch is on the far right##1
2. the malaysian is the malaysian##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3
4. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the dutch##3
5. the spanish is on the left or right of the british##3
6. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the british##3
7. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the snake##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |    4     |
| Nationality   | malaysian | spanish  | british | dutch |
| Pet           | pony     | snake | chinchilla    | hedgehog     |

