.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-14::.
There 4 different types of food: apricot, raspberry, zucchini, orange
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, chef, analyst, teacher
1. the person eating orange is on the left or right of the chef##3
2. the chef is on the right of the analyst##1
3. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the doctor##1
4. the chef is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating zucchini is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Food   | raspberry  | apricot | orange  | zucchini      |
| Job    | teacher | doctor | analyst | chef |

