.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, hiking, baking, board-games
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, trance, hip-hop, jazz
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far right##1
2. the fan of trance is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is the fan of jazz##1
4. the fan of trance is the person who's hobby is baking##1
5. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the fan of trance##3
6. the fan of hip-hop is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
7. the fan of trance is on the left or right of the fan of punk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | hiking | board-games | baking | fishing |
| Music-Genre   | jazz     | punk       | trance   | hip-hop      |

