.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-19::.
There 4 different types of food: banana, pepper, potato, cauliflower
The people have 4 different jobs:  firefighter, pilot, dressmaker, paramedic
1. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the dressmaker##1
2. the paramedic is on the left or right of the dressmaker##3
3. the pilot is on the left of the person eating pepper##1
4. the dressmaker is on the left of the person eating potato##1
5. the dressmaker is on the left of the pilot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1        |      2       |   3    |   4    |
| Food   | cauliflower        | banana       | potato   | pepper |
| Job    | paramedic | dressmaker | pilot | firefighter  |

