.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, tea, coffee, almond-milk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, ice-hockey, water-polo, biathlon
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
4. the person who's sport is golf is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the person who's sport is water-polo##3
6. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person drinking water##1
7. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person who's sport is water-polo##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | tea     | water     | coffee          | almond-milk |
| Sport      | golf | ice-hockey | biathlon | water-polo  |

 